===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{liushu|p}} or
{{liushu|ic|nocap=y}}: hand ({{zh-l|*又}}) holding a brush ([[𰀁]]). Originally referred to {{och-l|筆|writing brush}}; later {{liushu|j|nocap=y}} for {{och-l|聿|[[thereupon]]}}.

Unrelated to {{och-l|*建}}, in which the hand is holding a pole.

